name: Defy You
wikiSummary:
"Defy You" is a single by The Offspring featured in the 2002 movie, "Orange County," and first made an appearance on Orange County's original soundtrack released on December 18th, 2001. 
 The single was released by the band on the same date as the soundtrack.  The song later became available on the band's 2005 "Greatest Hits" compilation album.
